Name: Go, Go Cowboy
About the game: Go, Go Cowboy-Fast Top-Down-Shooter where the player acts as a Sheriff and clears randomly generated levels, with each level the enemies become more difficult, and the worlds are more hardcore, you can control a revolver or a saber, and after passing all the worlds you will get a Gatling machine Gun in your possession! Feature of game: - Hardcore - Pixel-Art - Random Generation Of Levels - Increasing Complexity - Boss
